Hi
I'm trying to create an image from canvas. Don't know how to extract surface from canvas to do it, so i   do:

        SKSurface surface = null;
        private void OnPaint(object sender, SkiaSharp.Views.Forms.SKPaintGLSurfaceEventArgs e)
        {
            mapDrawing.DrawSample(e.Surface.Canvas, e.RenderTarget.Width, e.RenderTarget.Height);

            surface = e.Surface;
        }

And then try to extract the snapshot from surface in another method after the first paint occurence:

        if (surface == null)
            return null;
  
                var snap = surface.Snapshot();
                var data = snap.Encode();
                byte[] bytearray = data.ToArray();
        }

and I get the expection when invoking surface.Snapshot();

```
